overview: PT Maintenance is the company you need when you need help at home. For over five years we provide to the citizens of London all possible services for their home. Our services include property inspection, plumbers, electricians, roof services, refurbishment, carpenters, decoration and painting services and much more. All our employees are specially trained and they will never let you down. You can rely on us almost every hour, because we work on extended work time when it’s needed and can come to your property even at evenings, holidays and weekends! Do not hesitate to call us or e-mail us for booking our services or just for a free quote!
